      <title>铝价承压，伦敦金属交易所关键价差再度飙升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/aluminum-squeeze-rolls-on-with-key-lme-spread-spiking-again</link>
      <description><![CDATA[铝市场压力持续增大，伦敦金属交易所 10 月份交割合约的溢价甚至高于 11 月份，表明铝市场供应紧张。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/aluminum-squeeze-rolls-on-with-key-lme-spread-spiking-again</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Oct 2024 13:12:20 GMT</pubDate>
